<section class="about">
	<div class="about__inner">
		<h1 class="about__heading">
			<span class="about__eyebrow">Celebrate the Los Angeles World Cup 26</span>
			<span class="about__title">Downtown Burbank Fan Zone</span>
		</h1>

		<div class="about__body">
			<p>This summer, the excitement of the world's game comes to the heart of Burbank.</p>

			<p>Downtown Burbank will host a Los Angeles World Cup 26 Fan Zone — a special registered experience featuring live match viewing and entertainment in a high-energy setting. The Fan Zone and festivities will take place along <strong>San Fernando Blvd. and surrounding streets in Downtown Burbank (from Magnolia Blvd. to Angeleno Ave.).</strong></p>

			<p>Alongside the Fan Zone, Downtown Burbank will come alive with a <strong>FREE international street fair</strong>, global flavors, cultural experiences, and special VIP offerings.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="about__newsletter">
			<a href="#footer_form" class="about__button">Sign Up for updates</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		background-color: var(--color-cream);
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.about__inner {
		max-width: 1250px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.about__heading {
		color: var(--color-coral);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		margin-top: 1em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75em;
	}

	.about__eyebrow {
		display: block;
		font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 3vw, 35px);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.1em;
	}

	.about__title {
		display: block;
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 58px);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.about__body {
		max-width: 780px;
		margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
		font-size: 17px;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--color-dark);
	}

	.about__body p {
		margin-bottom: 1.25em;
	}

	.about__body p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.about__newsletter {
		max-width: 780px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding-top: 1rem;
	}

	.about__button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		background-color: var(--color-coral);
		color: #fff;
		border: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-family: var(--font-family);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		text-decoration: none;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: filter 0.3s;
	}

	.about__button:hover {
		filter: brightness(1.1);
	}
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about__eyebrow {
			margin-bottom: 0.5em;
		}
		.about__heading
	}
</style>
